	<section id="1">
		<fragment id="1">
			<para>This group will define the content for the <link href="https://www.allette.com.au">www.allette.com.au</link> Website.</para>
			<heading level="2">Documents</heading>
			<para>The <xref id="884332" title="landing page" frag="default" reversefrag="1" reverselink="false" display="manual" type="none" uriid="175683" href="/ps/allette/www/website/landing.psml" urititle="Landing" mediatype="application/vnd.pageseeder.psml+xml" documenttype="references">landing page</xref> is a 'references' document which transcludes the content to display on the main page of the Website. The landing uses a specific template.</para>
			<para>All other document are either default documents or references documents. The templates on the Website are driven by block labels.</para>
			<heading level="2">Block labels</heading>
			<list>
				<item>
					<monospace>image-feature</monospace>  defines an image to display as a banner/masthead/hero image on a page. When referenced by the landing page, it is used as a feature image for linking. It MUST be defined first in the document in the <italic>title</italic> section.</item>
				<item>
					<monospace>image-side</monospace>  defines an image to display beside the fragment content on portfolio page.</item>
			</list>
		</fragment>
	</section>
